  "1805110": {
    "name": "太阳朋克：浮岛家园",
    "steam_appid": 1805110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《太阳朋克：浮岛家园 Solarpunk》是一款设定在一个科技高度发达、由漂浮岛屿组成的世界中的生存游戏。你可以独自一人或与朋友一起建造建筑、种植食物、制作工具，并驾驶自己的飞船探索遥远的天空之岛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用阳光、风力和水源建立能源系统，并自动化诸如收集资源和为植物浇水等流程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>🏠 自由建造</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用丰富的材料和装饰，自由设计你的梦想基地。打造温馨空间，添加个性化细节，让你的岛屿真正成为家。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/7cc5179a70e61d42cf06f296952cbd6a.poster.avif?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/7cc5179a70e61d42cf06f296952cbd6a.webm?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/7cc5179a70e61d42cf06f296952cbd6a.mp4?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些建筑是我们了不起的社区在试玩版中打造的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/ae878564d90e4b35c393e189e300e49c.avif?t=1772200075\" width=616 height=314 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/bfb6752cab8c9773011c7ceb72c21a8e.webp?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=9 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚡ 能源系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过风能和太阳能发电。天气状况会影响发电效率，因此需要提前规划。将能源储存在电池中，并使用无线供电让基地平稳运行。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/1f804d95ac068ab2108c3875528d240f.poster.avif?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/1f804d95ac068ab2108c3875528d240f.webm?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/1f804d95ac068ab2108c3875528d240f.mp4?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/bfb6752cab8c9773011c7ceb72c21a8e.webp?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=9 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👥 多人模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以单人游玩，也可以与朋友一起。每位玩家都有自己的背包，你们可以一起建造，也可以在空中建造属于自己的小天地。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/29f567dc7be4274f366af92f9eaf15a4.poster.avif?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/29f567dc7be4274f366af92f9eaf15a4.webm?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/29f567dc7be4274f366af92f9eaf15a4.mp4?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/bfb6752cab8c9773011c7ceb72c21a8e.webp?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=9 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🐷 动物与种植</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Solarpunk 中，你将与动物共生，而不是剥削。例如，如果你善待猪，它们可能会帮你挖出松露。水果和蔬菜是主要的食物来源：种下种子，等待成熟，然后收获。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/6488d28dab95058c4c133f0e70f276bc.poster.avif?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/6488d28dab95058c4c133f0e70f276bc.webm?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/6488d28dab95058c4c133f0e70f276bc.mp4?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/bfb6752cab8c9773011c7ceb72c21a8e.webp?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=9 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🤖 自动化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用运输无人机来自动完成资源采集等任务，让你有更多时间去建造和探索你的空中家园。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/b54969182dbd1e1f1e1fa6f6ede94ae0.poster.avif?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/b54969182dbd1e1f1e1fa6f6ede94ae0.webm?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/b54969182dbd1e1f1e1fa6f6ede94ae0.mp4?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/bfb6752cab8c9773011c7ceb72c21a8e.webp?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=9 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✈️ 飞船</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家都可以建造自己的飞船。使用它前往周边岛屿，发现全新的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/6eb77859af21a2f8a8780bc1c086778f.poster.avif?t=1772200075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/6eb77859af21a2f8a8780bc1c086778f.webm?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805110/extras/6eb77859af21a2f8a8780bc1c086778f.mp4?t=1772200075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
